                     <interp inst="t18460817-1639-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18460817-1639-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> stealing 50lbs. weight of peppercorns, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 17.; and 1 sack, is. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18460817-name-866" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-866" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
