                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 375.) I produce a certifi<lb></lb>cate of King's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Nov.</hi>, 1844; <hi rend="italic">and con<lb></lb>fined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
